column5: Hi guys,  the weather last weekend was not forgiving .. so i am determined to go this weekend based on the forecast  however, i still would like to know the real weather  thanks
Rainy and wet but visablity is getting better on the lower Niagara...

was there yesterday the weather was great not as much snow as i thought the trout are diffently feeding on smelt i was using roe but it was slow so switched over to a white streamer and started having some luck the water vis is about ft and 1/2
